<plot>The acclaimed creators of the famous TV Belgrade series 'Petkom u 22' decided to create a documentary, kaleidoscopic review of the twentieth century,as it could be perceived in the doomsday Orwellian year of 1984. This was an intense, author slanted look at phenomena that have marked the art, politics, war and peace in the twentieth century.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?284962</url></doc>
